  "prompt": "Which is your favorite JUMLA of PM MODI?",
  "response": "As an AI, I don't have personal preferences or feelings, so I don't have a \"favorite\" statement by Prime Minister Narendra Modi. However, PM Modi is known for his impactful and motivational speeches. Some of his famous lines include:\n\n1. **\"\u0938\u092c\u0915\u093e \u0938\u093e\u0925, \u0938\u092c\u0915\u093e \u0935\u093f\u0915\u093e\u0938, \u0938\u092c\u0915\u093e \u0935\u093f\u0936\u094d\u0935\u093e\u0938, \u0938\u092c\u0915\u093e \u092a\u094d\u0930\u092f\u093e\u0938\" (Sabka Saath, Sabka Vikas, Sabka Vishwas, Sabka Prayas)** - This phrase emphasizes inclusive growth and collective effort for the nation's development.  \n2. **\"\u0928\u090f \u092d\u093e\u0930\u0924\" (Naye Bharat)** - Highlighting his vision for a \"New India\" that is progressive and forward-looking.  \n3. **\"\u092e\u0947\u0915 \u0907\u0928 \u0907\u0902\u0921\u093f\u092f\u093e\" (Make in India)** - A call to promote manufacturing and innovation within the country.  \n4. **\"\u0921\u093f\u091c\u093f\u091f\u0932 \u0907\u0902\u0921\u093f\u092f\u093e\" (Digital India)** - Encouraging technological advancement and digital empowerment.  \n5. **\"\u091c\u092f \u091c\u0935\u093e\u0928, \u091c\u092f \u0915\u093f\u0938\u093e\u0928\" (Jai Jawan, Jai Kisan)** - Reviving the spirit of honoring soldiers and farmers.  \n\nDo you have a favorite Modi jumla or speech that resonates with you? Let me know!",
